OL,3,CElderly woman seriously injured in
OL,4,Cpark sex attack
OL,6,FA 25-year-old man has been arrested
OL,7,Fover the attempted rape of an elderly
OL,8,Fwoman in a Sheffield park.
OL,10,FThe woman, in her 70s, was attacked as
OL,11,Fshe walked through Concord Park at
OL,12,Faround 7.26am on Wednesday.
OL,14,FShe was taken to hospital with serious
OL,15,Finjuries.
OL,17,FInsp Alec Gibbons, of South Yorkshire
OL,18,FPolice, said extra patrols were being
OL,19,Fcarried out in the Shiregreen area of
OL,20,Fthe city.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
