OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774541483
OL,3,CElderly woman seriously injured in
OL,4,Cpark sex attack
OL,6,FHe said: "The victim is receiving
OL,7,Fsupport from officers and trained
OL,8,Fmedical professionals, and we have put
OL,9,Fextra patrols in place in the local
OL,10,Farea.
OL,12,F"We understand that news of this
OL,13,Fincident will cause concern in the
OL,14,Flocal community and I would urge
OL,15,Fanyone with questions or concerns to
OL,16,Fplease speak to our officers on the
OL,17,Fground - they are there to help you
OL,18,Fand keep you safe."
OL,20,FWitnesses are being urged to come
OL,21,Fforward.
